Notes.Text:
This update for ruby2.5 fixes the following issues:

- Update to 2.5.9
- CVE-2021-28965: XML round-trip vulnerability in REXML (bsc#1184644)

Vulnerabilities.Description: The REXML gem before 3.2.5 in Ruby before 2.6.7, 2.7.x before 2.7.3, and 3.x before 3.0.1 does not properly address XML round-trip issues. An incorrect document can be produced after parsing and serializing.
